content:
After reviewing the story, I've found that all the names of the hexagrams in the story are consistent with the new translation we've been working on. Here's a list of the hexagrams and their names in the story:

2. Receptive
3. Difficulty at the Beginning
4. Naivety
5. Waiting
6. Conflict
7. Unified Action
8. Solidarity
9. Taming the Power of the Small
10. Care
11. Peace
12. Standstill
13. Fellowship
14. Possession in Great Measure
15. Humility
16. Enthusiasm
17. Following
18. Correcting
19. Approach
20. Contemplation
21. Biting Through
22. Grace
23. Splitting Apart
24. Return
25. Innocence
26. Taming the Power of the Great
27. Nourishment
28. Greatness in Excess
29. The Abysmal
30. The Clinging
31. Influence
32. Duration
33. Retreat
34. Great Power

40. Deliverance
41. Decrease
42. Increase
43. Breakthrough
44. Coming to Meet
45. Gathering Together
46. Pushing Upward

Please let me know if you find any discrepancies or if you would like any changes.
